================================================================================
MODIFICATIONS FROM ORIGINAL

Significant enhancements include:
- Runtime migration from Node.js to Bun
- Image processing rewrite with GraphicsMagick dithering
- Cron-based scheduler system with Web UI
- Various optimizations and improvements
- Expanded device preset support (38+ devices)

================================================================================
